{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T04:24:10.257Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the official Claude Cookbook documentation and the Claude API course, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Routing\""},{"type":"text","text":" is a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"multi-LLM workflow pattern that dynamically selects specialized processing paths based on input characteristics"},{"type":"text","text":", similar to how a router directs internet traffic to the right server."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Routing takes the user's original input and feeds it into a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"routing step"},{"type":"text","text":" (usually a call to Claude) that "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"categorizes the task"},{"type":"text","text":", then forwards the input to a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"particular follow-up processing pipeline"},{"type":"text","text":" specialized for that task type."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Basic Flow"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"User Input → Router (Claude categorizes) → Route Decision → Specialized Pipeline → Final Output"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"What Happens"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Routing step"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude categorizes user input/task into predefined categories"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Route decision"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on classification, select which pipeline to use"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Specialized pipeline"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Forward to customized prompt/tools/workflow for that category"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Final output"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Processed result from the specialized pipeline"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How It Works"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The routing pattern follows a clear sequence:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prepare user request"},{"type":"text","text":" — Send original input to the router"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Router classifies"},{"type":"text","text":" — Claude instance with strict system prompt categorizes the intent"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Select pipeline"},{"type":"text","text":" — Based on classification, route to specific workflow"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Execute specialized pipeline"},{"type":"text","text":" — Each route has its own custom prompt, tools, and workflow"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Return result"},{"type":"text","text":" — Final output from the specialized pipeline"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example: Video Script Generator"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- User asks: \"Python functions\"\n- Router categorizes: → "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Educational"},{"type":"text","text":" (vs. Entertainment, Documentary, etc.)\n- Route to: Educational video pipeline\n- Pipeline writes: Script with clear explanations, thought-provoking examples, educational tone\n- Output: Educational video script about Python functions"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Semantic Routing (Advanced)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Modern routing uses "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"semantic embeddings"},{"type":"text","text":" to match task intent to agent capabilities:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Phase"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"What Happens"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Agent Registration"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Plugin generates semantic embeddings from agent capability descriptions using Claude Opus"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Task Intake"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Natural language task wrapped with context: codebase files, conversation history, tool access"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Intent Embedding"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Router sends task description to Claude Opus for semantic embedding generation (500ms-1s)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Capability Matching"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Compute cosine similarity between task embedding and agent capability embeddings (~100ms)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Load Balancing"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Adjust scores: penalize overloaded agents, prioritize available ones (~50ms)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Route Decision"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispatch to highest-scoring available agent with task context (~50ms)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Result Verification"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Evaluate output relevance; if poor match, trigger re-routing (1-2 sec)"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key metric"},{"type":"text","text":": Semantic routing improves first-attempt match rates to "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"85%+"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"When to Use It"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Routing is ideal when:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Condition"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why Routing Helps"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Different task types need different approaches"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Each category gets specialized handling"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Intents vary widely across inputs"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Router determines which path to take"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Need specialized tools/prompts per category"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Each route has custom configuration"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Want to optimize cost/performance"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Route simple tasks to cheaper models, complex to powerful ones"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multi-agent system with specialists"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Route to agent with highest domain expertise"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Routing vs. Prompt Chaining vs. Parallelization"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The three basic multi-LLM workflow patterns:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pattern"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"How It Works"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"When to Use"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt Chaining"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sequential subtasks, each builds on previous"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Task needs step-by-step transformation"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Parallelization"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Independent subtasks across multiple LLMs concurrently"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Subtasks don't depend on each other"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Routing"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dynamically selects specialized path based on input"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Different task types need different approaches"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"State-Based Routing (Advanced)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Routing can also be "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"state-based"},{"type":"text","text":", where the next agent/action depends on project state:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# routing.yaml example\nMode: NOUVEAU (no .plan/ directory)\n  Trigger: First run on new project\n  Next Agent: instructor\n  Action: Ask discovery questions\n\nMode: EN_COURS (recent .plan/, modified <7 days)\n  Trigger: Resuming active project\n  Next Agent: Determined by state.json.current_phase\n  Action: Continue from where left off\n\nMode: REPRISE (old .plan/, modified >7 days)\n  Trigger: Resuming abandoned project\n  Next Agent: instructor\n  Action: Audit architecture, check for obsolescence"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Phase transitions"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"discovery (completed) → architecture phase → architect\narchitecture (completed) → check gate → user_approval → ✓ Approved → implementation → executor\nimplementation (completed) → validation → writor\nvalidation (completed) → check gate → user_approval → ✓ Approved → complete"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mental Model"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Think of routing like a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"hospital triage system"},{"type":"text","text":": patients arrive, a nurse (router) assesses their condition and categorizes them, then routes them to the appropriate specialist (cardiologist, orthopedist, neurologist) who has the right tools and expertise for that specific problem."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Takeaways"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Routing dynamically selects specialized LLM paths based on input characteristics"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Takes user input → classifies it → routes to specialized pipeline"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Router is usually a Claude instance with strict system prompt for categorization"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Each route has its own custom prompt, tools, and workflow"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Semantic routing uses embeddings to match task intent to agent capabilities (85%+ match rate)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Can be state-based: route depends on project state, phase, blockers, gates"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"One of three basic multi-LLM patterns: Prompt Chaining, Parallelization, Routing"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Useful for: video generators, multi-agent systems, task classifiers, content pipelines"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Trades cost/latency for improved performance on varying task types"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Routing is the orchestration mechanism that directs diverse inputs to the right specialized processors, enabling Claude to handle varied task types efficiently."}]}]}}
